`sum_at_correct` ‚Äî on the measure `n.val.size - i.toNat`, threads the invariant `acc.toInt = cond_sum_int n i.toNat`, splits on the compound parity condition, discharges the signed `+?` no-overflow via the `hfit` precondition on `cond_sum_int n (i+1)`.

